# Top 20 OS Interview Questions – Page Replacement Algorithms

1. What is page replacement?
2. Why do we need page replacement algorithms?
3. What is a page fault?
4. What is page hit and page miss?
5. Explain FIFO page replacement.
6. What is Belady’s anomaly?
7. Explain Optimal (OPT) page replacement.
8. Why is OPT not used in real systems?
9. Explain LRU (Least Recently Used).
10. Explain LFU (Least Frequently Used).
11. Explain MFU (Most Frequently Used).
12. What is NRU (Not Recently Used)?
13. What is second chance algorithm?
14. Explain clock page replacement.
15. What is the difference between LRU and LFU?
16. What is the difference between FIFO and LRU?
17. Why do page replacement algorithms matter?
18. What is the impact of page size on replacement performance?
19. How does working set affect page replacement?
20. What are advantages and disadvantages of different page replacement algorithms?
